        "text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Rooted in the Japanese concept of shinogi—the ridgeline or backbone of a blade—Case 15-25 applies the principles of strength, balance, and integrity to equipment for professionals. Founded by chef Matt Abergel and shaped by a deep respect for Japanese craftsmanship, it represents a decade of research, development, and refinement (2015–2025), resulting in a knife case built to endure time, movement, and daily wear.</p>"
